        "setup": "Create or install a HubSpot app with `auth.type=oauth` in your app config, then complete the HubSpot OAuth install flow for the target account. The resulting `Bearer` access token is what you send to HubSpot APIs. HubSpot documents OAuth as the path for multi-account installs and notes that app users must authorize the app. See the [authentication overview](https://developers.hubspot.com/docs/apps/developer-platform/build-apps/authentication/overview).",
